        <h2 class="display-4 text-center mb-4" style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold;">What Our Clients Say</h2>
        <div class="testimonial-carousel" style="display: flex; overflow: hidden; gap: 30px; justify-content: center;">
            <div class="testimonial-item" style="background: #333; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); max-width: 300px; text-align: center;">
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic;">"This system has transformed our HR department. It’s user-friendly, fast, and intuitive. Managing employee data has never been easier!"</p>
