            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-item" style="background: #333; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); max-width: 300px; text-align: center;">
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic;">"We saw an immediate improvement in our payroll processing efficiency. The software's automation features saved us countless hours."</p>
                <footer style="font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px;">- Jane Smith, Payroll Director</footer>
